应用介绍：
校体云（青少年体质健康管理系统）——为中小学生提供体质健康的监测、检测、采集、数据分析、数据平台、运动处方、体育课改等一系列学校体育信息化与学生体质健康整体解决方案。

【产品特点】
@提升学生体质健康，专家团队专业分析
@体测体质 语系转换丨发现孩子体质弱项，针对性改善
@定制化 改善方案丨让每个学生都有自己的运动“私教”
@个性化 健康食谱丨绘制孩子专属生长曲线，专业有营养
@AI科技 体感运动丨 精准动作识别 实时智能纠错

一句话简介：校体云----青少年体质健康管理系统

"Chinese character strokes" input Chinese characters to search, you can view the radicals, stroke breakdown, related words and stroke order animations of this Chinese character. "Chinese characters strokes" is equipped with Chinese characters and word dictation functions to solve the distress of dictating Chinese characters over and over for parents of elementary school students ! If you are learning Chinese characters, I believe that "Chinese character stroke order" will make learning Chinese characters easier!
Special feature
· Synchronous new words for elementary school textbooks;
· The sequence of Chinese character strokes is displayed in the form of animation;
· Chinese character dictation, consolidation exercises;
・You can view the detailed description of Chinese characters, including related groups of words, explanations, related ancient poems, etc.;
・Can collect any Chinese characters to facilitate review;
· Follow Chinese characters and master the correct writing order of Chinese characters;

Finally, if you have any usage problems or need to add other textbook fonts, you can give us feedback in the app, and we will continue to optimize and improve.

